description:
At the 2023 Sohn Investment Conference on May 9, 2023, Stripe CEO Patrick Collison spoke with OpenAI CEO Sam Altman about the future of AI and more. Introduced by Sohn Conference Foundation Chair Graham Duncan.

This session is presented by Sohn 2023 Corporate Sponsor: Tegus
title: Sohn 2023 | Patrick Collison in conversation Sam Altman
